1513:../../Drivers/CMSIS/Include/core_cm4.h ****   \defgroup   CMSIS_core_bitfield     Core register bit field macros
1514:../../Drivers/CMSIS/Include/core_cm4.h ****   \brief      Macros for use with bit field definitions (xxx_Pos, xxx_Msk).
